snippet.title: The Truth About The Little Couple's Dr. Jen Arnold
snippet.description:
Since 2009, viewers of TLC’s The Little Couple have followed married couple Jen and Bill Arnold through the ups and downs of their lives, including adopting two children.

Jen Arnold is a doctor, as well as a medical director at Johns Hopkins All Children’s Hospital, but there is a lot more about her that you don’t get to see on the show. For example, she and Bill actually met once when they were just kids, although they wouldn’t be properly introduced until years later.

Let’s take a look at the truth about Dr. Jen Arnold, star of TLC’s The Little Couple.
